s://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=scientific%20heatmap%20blue&w=1200&h=800\",\n                R2: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=data%20heatmap%20cyan&w=1200&h=800\",\n                RMSE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=error%20map%20orange&w=1200&h=800\",\n                MAE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=terrain%20error%20analysis&w=1200&h=800\",\n                umbral: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=threshold%20map%20science&w=1200&h=800\"\n              },\n              hex: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=hexbin%20analysis%20chart&w=900&h=600\",\n              error: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=remote%20sensing%20error%20plot&w=900&h=600\",\n              plot: \"https://example.com\"\n            },\n            PS: {\n              stats: {\n                R: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=scientific%20scatter%20blue&w=1200&h=800\",\n                R2: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=correlation%20dashboard%20teal&w=1200&h=800\",\n                RMSE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=analytics%20surface%20orange&w=1200&h=800\",\n                MAE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=quantitative%20surface%20chart&w=1200&h=800\",\n                umbral: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=threshold%20classification%20map&w=1200&h=800\"\n              },\n              hex: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=hexagonal%20scientific%20visualization&w=900&h=600\",\n              error: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=distribution%20error%20diagram&w=900&h=600\",\n              plot: \"https://example.com\"\n            }\n          },\n          B03: {\n            S2: {\n              stats: {\n                R: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=green%20spectral%20analysis&w=1200&h=800\",\n                R2: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=statistical%20field%20map&w=1200&h=800\",\n                RMSE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=residual%20landscape%20map&w=1200&h=800\",\n                MAE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=agro%20analytics%20result&w=1200&h=800\",\n                umbral: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=classification%20zones%20map&w=1200&h=800\"\n              },\n              hex: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=geospatial%20hexbin%20green&w=900&h=600\",\n              error: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=error%20density%20green&w=900&h=600\",\n              plot: \"https://example.com\"\n            },\n            PS: {\n              stats: {\n                R: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=planet%20sensor%20comparison&w=1200&h=800\",\n                R2: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=regression%20map%20green&w=1200&h=800\",\n                RMSE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=rmse%20cartography&w=1200&h=800\",\n                MAE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=mae%20analysis%20map&w=1200&h=800\",\n                umbral: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=threshold%20science%20green&w=1200&h=800\"\n              },\n              hex: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=green%20hexbin%20stats&w=900&h=600\",\n              error: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=green%20error%20visual&w=900&h=600\",\n              plot: \"https://example.com\"\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        id: \"Escena Sur\",\n        date: \"2024-05-28\",\n        lat: -36.82,\n        lon: -73.05,\n        reference: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=coastal%20satellite%20imagery&w=900&h=700\",\n        bands: {\n          B04: {\n            S2: {\n              stats: {\n                R: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=red%20band%20analysis%20map&w=1200&h=800\",\n                R2: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=red%20correlation%20surface&w=1200&h=800\",\n                RMSE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=marine%20rmse%20map&w=1200&h=800\",\n                MAE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=marine%20mae%20map&w=1200&h=800\",\n                umbral: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=coastal%20threshold%20map&w=1200&h=800\"\n              },\n              hex: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=red%20hexbin%20coast&w=900&h=600\",\n              error: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=marine%20error%20chart&w=900&h=600\",\n              plot: \"https://example.com\"\n            },\n            PS: {\n              stats: {\n                R: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=coastal%20regression%20dashboard&w=1200&h=800\",\n                R2: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=coastal%20correlation%20map&w=1200&h=800\",\n                RMSE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=coastal%20rmse%20dashboard&w=1200&h=800\",\n                MAE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=coastal%20mae%20dashboard&w=1200&h=800\",\n                umbral: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=coastal%20threshold%20dashboard&w=1200&h=800\"\n              },\n              hex: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=coastal%20hexagonal%20analysis&w=900&h=600\",\n              error: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=ocean%20error%20density&w=900&h=600\",\n              plot: \"https://example.com\"\n            }\n          },\n          B08: {\n            S2: {\n              stats: {\n                R: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20analysis%20remote%20sensing&w=1200&h=800\",\n                R2: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20correlation%20map&w=1200&h=800\",\n                RMSE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20rmse%20surface&w=1200&h=800\",\n                MAE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20mae%20surface&w=1200&h=800\",\n                umbral: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20threshold%20map&w=1200&h=800\"\n              },\n              hex: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20hexbin%20scientific&w=900&h=600\",\n              error: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20residual%20distribution&w=900&h=600\",\n              plot: \"https://example.com\"\n            },\n            PS: {\n              stats: {\n                R: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20planet%20analysis&w=1200&h=800\",\n                R2: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20planet%20correlation&w=1200&h=800\",\n                RMSE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20planet%20rmse&w=1200&h=800\",\n                MAE: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20planet%20mae&w=1200&h=800\",\n                umbral: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=nir%20planet%20threshold&w=1200&h=800\"\n              },\n              hex: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=infrared%20hexbin%20chart&w=900&h=600\",\n              error: \"https://app.grapesjs.com/api/assets/random-image?query=infrared%20error%20chart&w=900&h=600\",\n              plot: \"https://example.com\"\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    ];\n\n    let catalogo = [];\n    let map;\n    let currentMarker = null;\n\n    const selImg = document.getElementById(\"imagen\");\n    const selTipo = document.getElementById(\"tipo\");\n    const selBanda = document.getElementById(\"banda\");\n    const selStat = document.getElementById(\"stat_type\");\n    const refImg = document.getElementById(\"ref\");\n    const statsImg = document.getElementById(\"stats_img\");\n    const hexImg = document.getElementById(\"hex\");\n    const errorImg = document.getElementById(\"error\");\n    const plotFrame = document.getElementById(\"plot\");\n    const tabla = document.getElementById(\"tabla\");\n    const modal = document.getElementById(\"modal\");\n    const modalContent = document.getElementById(\"modal_content\");\n    const modalTitle = document.getElementById(\"modal_title\");\n\n    function fadeUpdate(element, newSrc) {\n      element.classList.add(\"fade-out\");\n      setTimeout(() => {\n        if (element.tagName === \"IFRAME\") {\n          element.src = newSrc || \"\";\n        } else {\n          element.src = newSrc || \"\";\n        }\n        element.classList.remove(\"fade-out\");\n      }, 180);\n    }\n\n    function initMap() {\n      map = L.map('map', { zoomControl: true }).setView([-35, -71], 5);\n      L.tileLayer('https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.fr/hot/{z}/{x}/{y}.png', {\n        attribution: '&copy; OpenStreetMap contributors'\n      }).addTo(map);\n    }\n\n    function fillImageSelect() {\n      selImg.innerHTML = \"\";\n      catalogo.forEach((item, index) => {\n        const option = document.createElement(\"option\");\n        option.value = index;\n        option.textContent = item.id;\n        selImg.appendChild(option);\n      });\n    }\n\n    function fillBandSelect() {\n      const scene = catalogo[Number(selImg.value)] || catalogo[0];\n      const bandKeys = Object.keys(scene.bands || {});\n      selBanda.innerHTML = \"\";\n      bandKeys.forEach(band => {\n        const option = document.createElement(\"option\");\n        option.value = band;\n        option.textContent = band;\n        selBanda.appendChild(option);\n      });\n    }\n\n    function currentScene() {\n      return catalogo[Number(selImg.value)] || catalogo[0];\n    }\n\n    function currentPayload() {\n      const scene = currentScene();\n      const band = selBanda.value;\n      const type = selTipo.value;\n      const metric = selStat.value;\n      const bandData = scene?.bands?.[band];\n      const typeData = bandData?.[type];\n      return { scene, band, type, metric, bandData, typeData };\n    }\n\n    function updateMap(scene) {\n      const lat = scene.lat;\n      const lon = scene.lon;\n      document.getElementById(\"meta_lat\").textContent = lat.toFixed(4);\n      document.getElementById(\"meta_lon\").textContent = lon.toFixed(4);\n\n      if (currentMarker) {\n        map.removeLayer(currentMarker);\n      }\n\n      currentMarker = L.marker([lat, lon]).addTo(map);\n      currentMarker.bindPopup(`<strong>${scene.id}</strong><br>${scene.date}`).openPopup();\n      map.setView([lat, lon], 8);\n      setTimeout(() => map.invalidateSize(), 250);\n    }\n\n    function updateTable(scene, band, type, metric) {\n      const rows = [\n        [\"Escena\", scene.id, \"Valor principal\"],\n        [\"Fecha\", scene.date, \"Metadato auxiliar\"],\n        [\"Latitud\", scene.lat.toFixed(4), \"Metadato auxiliar\"],\n        [\"Longitud\", scene.lon.toFixed(4), \"Metadato auxiliar\"],\n        [\"Comparación\", type === \"S2\" ? \"S2 vs S2DR3\" : \"PS vs S2DR3\", \"Valor principal\"],\n        [\"Banda\", band, \"Valor principal\"],\n        [\"Métrica\", metric, \"Valor principal\"]\n      ];\n\n      tabla.innerHTML = `\n        <table data-gjs-name=\"Data Table\" class=\"min-w-full border-separate border-spacing-0 text-left\">\n          <thead data-gjs-name=\"Table Head\" class=\"sticky top-0 z-10 bg-slate-100\">\n            <tr data-gjs-name=\"Table Row\">\n              <th data-gjs-name=\"Table Header\" class=\"border-b border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Campo</th>\n              <th data-gjs-name=\"Table Header\" class=\"border-b border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Valor</th>\n              <th data-gjs-name=\"Table Header\" class=\"border-b border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Categoría</th>\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody data-gjs-name=\"Table Body\" class=\"bg-white\">\n            ${rows.map((row, index) => `\n              <tr data-gjs-name=\"Table Row\" class=\"${index % 2 === 0 ? 'bg-white' : 'bg-slate-50/70'}\">\n                <td data-gjs-name=\"Table Cell\" class=\"border-b border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800\">${row[0]}</td>\n                <td data-gjs-name=\"Table Cell\" class=\"border-b border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-700\">${row[1]}</td>\n                <td data-gjs-name=\"Table Cell\" class=\"border-b border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 text-sm\">\n                  <span data-gjs-name=\"Table Badge\" class=\"inline-flex rounded-full ${row[2] === 'Valor principal' ? 'border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700' : 'border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600'} px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold\">${row[2]}</span>\n                </td>\n              </tr>`).join(\"\")}\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      `;\n    }\n\n    function updateUI() {\n      const { scene, band, type, metric, typeData } = currentPayload();\n      if (!scene || !typeData) return;\n\n      document.getElementById(\"meta_scene\").textContent = scene.id;\n      document.getElementById(\"meta_date\").textContent = scene.date;\n      document.getElementById(\"meta_type\").textContent = type === \"S2\" ? \"S2 vs S2DR3\" : \"PS vs S2DR3\";\n      document.getElementById(\"meta_band\").textContent = band;\n      document.getElementById(\"meta_metric\").textContent = metric;\n\n      fadeUpdate(refImg, scene.reference);\n      fadeUpdate(statsImg, typeData.stats?.[metric] || \"\");\n      fadeUpdate(hexImg, typeData.hex || \"\");\n      fadeUpdate(errorImg, typeData.error || \"\");\n      fadeUpdate(plotFrame, typeData.plot || \"about:blank\");\n\n      updateMap(scene);\n      updateTable(scene, band, type, metric);\n    }\n\n    function attachMediaOpeners() {\n      function openImage(title, src, alt) {\n        modalTitle.textContent = title;\n        modalContent.innerHTML = `<img data-gjs-name=\"Modal Image\" src=\"${src}\" alt=\"${alt || title}\" class=\"max-h-[78vh] w-full rounded-2xl object-contain\">`;\n        modal.classList.remove(\"hidden\");\n        modal.classList.add(\"flex\");\n        document.body.classList.add(\"modal-open\");\n      }\n\n      function openFrame(title, src) {\n        modalTitle.textContent = title;\n        modalContent.innerHTML = `<iframe data-gjs-name=\"Modal Iframe\" src=\"${src}\" title=\"${title}\" class=\"h-[78vh] w-full rounded-2xl bg-white\"></iframe>`;\n        modal.classList.remove(\"hidden\");\n        modal.classList.add(\"flex\");\n        document.body.classList.add(\"modal-open\");\n      }\n\n      document.getElementById(\"open_ref\").addEventListener(\"click\", () => openImage(\"Imagen de referencia\", refImg.src, \"Imagen de referencia\"));\n      document.getElementById(\"open_stats\").addEventListener(\"click\", () => openImage(\"Resultados generales\", statsImg.src, \"Resultados generales\"));\n      document.getElementById(\"open_hex\").addEventListener(\"click\", () => openImage(\"Hexbin\", hexImg.src, \"Hexbin\"));\n      document.getElementById(\"open_error\").addEventListener(\"click\", () => openImage(\"Error\", errorImg.src, \"Error\"));\n      document.getElementById(\"open_plot\").addEventListener(\"click\", () => openFrame(\"Plot interactivo\", plotFrame.src));\n\n      refImg.addEventListener(\"click\", () => openImage(\"Imagen de referencia\", refImg.src, \"Imagen de referencia\"));\n      statsImg.addEventListener(\"click\", () => openImage(\"Resultados generales\", statsImg.src, \"Resultados generales\"));\n      hexImg.addEventListener(\"click\", () => openImage(\"Hexbin\", hexImg.src, \"Hexbin\"));\n      errorImg.addEventListener(\"click\", () => openImage(\"Error\", errorImg.src, \"Error\"));\n      plotFrame.addEventListener(\"click\", () => openFrame(\"Plot interactivo\", plotFrame.src));\n\n      document.getElementById(\"close_modal\").addEventListener(\"click\", closeModal);\n      modal.addEventListener(\"click\", (e) => {\n        if (e.target === modal) closeModal();\n      });\n      document.addEventListener(\"keydown\", (e) => {\n        if (e.key === \"Escape\") closeModal();\n      });\n    }\n\n    function closeModal() {\n      modal.classList.add(\"hidden\");\n      modal.classList.remove(\"flex\");\n      modalContent.innerHTML = \"\";\n      document.body.classList.remove(\"modal-open\");\n    }\n\n    function bindEvents() {\n      selImg.addEventListener(\"change\", () => {\n        fillBandSelect();\n        updateUI();\n      });\n      selTipo.addEventListener(\"change\", updateUI);\n      selBanda.addEventListener(\"change\", updateUI);\n      selStat.addEventListener(\"change\", updateUI);\n    }\n\n    function startApp(data) {\n      catalogo = Array.isArray(data) && data.length ? data : fallbackCatalog;\n      initMap();\n      fillImageSelect();\n      fillBandSelect();\n      bindEvents();\n      attachMediaOpeners();\n      updateUI();\n    }\n\n    fetch(\"catalogo_final.json\")\n      .then(r => r.ok ? r.json() : Promise.reject())\n      .then(data => startApp(data))\n      .catch(() => startApp(fallbackCatalog));\n  "}]}],"doctype":"<!DOCTYPE html>","head":{"type":"head","components":[{"tagName":"meta","void":true,"attributes":{"charset":"UTF-8"}},{"tagName":"meta","void":true,"attributes":{"name":"viewport","content":"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"}},{"tagName":"title","type":"text","components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Interfaz de resultados"}]},{"tagName":"link","void":true,"attributes":{"rel":"preconnect","href":"https://fonts.googleapis.com"}},{"tagName":"link","void":true,"attributes":{"rel":"preconnect","href":"https://fonts.gstatic.com","crossorigin":""}},{"tagName":"link","void":true,"attributes":{"href":"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Fraunces:wght@600;700&display=swap","rel":"stylesheet"}},{"tagName":"link","void":true,"attributes":{"rel":"stylesheet","href":"https://unpkg.com/leaflet/dist/leaflet.css"}},{"type":"script","attributes":{"src":"https://unpkg.com/leaflet/dist/leaflet.js"}}]},"docEl":{"tagName":"html","attributes":{"lang":"es"}}},"id":"AH73xsWxRWVcdFEm","minHeight":"500px"}],"id":"zizqwF0U07FQ3Bcw"}],"symbols":[{"tagName":"main","name":"Main Content","classes":["main-content"],"attributes":{"id":"iv4mp-2"},"__symbols":["iv4mp"],"components":[{"tagName":"section","name":"Top Grid","classes":["stats-grid"],"attributes":{"id":"ihzlj-2"},"__symbols":["ihzlj"],"components":[{"tagName":"article","name":"Map Card","classes":["panel-shadow","gjs-t-border","map-card"],"attributes":{"id":"igsitn"},"__symbols":["ikosf"],"components":[{"name":"Card Header","classes":["card-header"],"attributes":{"id":"im717g"},"__symbols":["i9dtd"],"components":[{"name":"Header Text","classes":["header-text"],"attributes":{"id":"iizrwx"},"__symbols":["iuzzw"],"components":[{"tagName":"h2","type":"heading","name":"Section Title","classes":["gjs-t-h2","section-title"],"attributes":{"id":"i03skd"},"__symbols":["ikb0l"],"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Mapa","attributes":{"id":"idh442"},"__symbols":["ix2mh"]}]},{"tagName":"p","type":"text","name":"Section Subtitle","classes":["section-subtitle"],"attributes":{"id":"it3str"},"__symbols":["ifls